2005-11-23 Daniel Willkomm
	* L2Address.h: created base class for layer 2 addresses; Just contains one
	parameter, namely the nic module id()
	* L3Address.h: created base class for layer 3 addresses; Just contains one
	parameter, namely the netw module id()
	* MacControlInfo.h: exracted MacControlInfo from NetwPkt.msg into an own
	file
	* ApplControlInfo.h: added a control info to exchange L3 addresses between
	network and application layer
